        public LevelInfo(int nrOfTroops,

        Constructor that initiates the object with the given parameters.
        Parameters:
        nrOfTroops - The number of troops to create at the current level.
        creatureCost - The base cost for creatures at the current level.
        teleporterCost - The teleporter cost for creatures at the current level.
        startCredit - The attacking player's start credit at the current level
        levelName - The current level's name.
